name: NARUTON ON TON
description: Naruto is a legendary tale of ambition, friendship, and perseverance set in a world where ninja clans vie for power and honor. Created by Masashi Kishimoto, this epic manga series follows the journey of Naruto Uzumaki, a young ninja with dreams of becoming the strongest ninja and leader of his village, known as the Hokage.
